sec.p:
Lawyer Erin Bruner (

Laura Linney
) takes on the church and the state when she fights in defense of a priest, Father Richard Moore (

Tom Wilkinson
) who performed an 
exorcism on a young woman, Emily Rose (

Jennifer Carpenter
). Bruner must battle the state lawyer as well as her own loneliness, as she realizes that her career so far has not fulfilled her. She takes the case, albeit reluctantly, because she believes it will elevate her to senior partner at her law firm.  The priest agrees to let her defend him only if he is allowed to tell Emily's story.
